<h2>Advanced Search Tips</h2>
      <p class="advanced-help-topic">Use search fields to find specific information and select facets in the left-hand menu to limit the scope of your search.</p>
      <p class="advanced-help-topic">Search for a specific phrase by surrounding it with quotation marks.</p>
      <p class="advanced-example-heading">Example:</p>
      <pre class="advanced-example">"grapes of wrath"</pre>
      <p class="advanced-help-topic">Use uppercase OR, AND, and NOT to create complex searches.</p>
      <p class="advanced-example-heading">Examples:</p>
      <pre class="advanced-example">"frida kahlo" AND exhibitions</pre>
      <pre class="advanced-example">kyoto NOT protocol</pre>
    <p class="advanced-help-topic">Use parentheses to group logical sections of your search.</p>
    <p class="advanced-example-heading">Example:</p>        
    <pre class="advanced-example">(gay OR lesbian OR transgender) sports</pre>


